Module com.augursolutions.wordler
Package com.augursolutions.wordler

Class SpellingBeeSolver.SpellingBeeSolution

java.lang.Object
com.augursolutions.wordler.SpellingBeeSolver.SpellingBeeSolution
Enclosing class:
SpellingBeeSolver
public static class SpellingBeeSolver.SpellingBeeSolution extends Object
Holds the solution set to a Spelling Bee puzzle. Set of all answers is stored as a Dictionary object in allAnsers. All answers that are pangrams (i.e. use all letters in the puzzle) are stored as an ArrayList<Word> in pangrams. Answers are also organized by word length in answersByLength
